## Frontend (Vite)
# Supabase Project URL from Supabase dashboard: Settings → API → Project URL
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://<your-project-ref>.supabase.co
# Supabase anon public key: Settings → API → Project API keys → anon public
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<your-anon-public-key>

VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

## Backend (recommended)
# Use the same Project URL (not the Postgres host)
SUPABASE_URL=https://<your-project-ref>.supabase.co
# Backend should use service role key for inserts if RLS is enabled:
# Settings → API → Project API keys → service_role (keep private)
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=<your-service-role-key>
